Matchbox car, then, will you?

32:13.932 --> 32:15.368
Come on.

32:15.542 --> 32:17.283
Coming.

32:18.501 --> 32:20.242
-Do you want to join a gang?
-I'm not allowed.

32:20.416 --> 32:22.810
-Why not?
-My mother said she'd kill me.

32:22.984 --> 32:25.117
Sure she doesn't have to know.
That's the whole point.

32:25.291 --> 32:26.640
-Are you in one?
-Aye.

32:26.814 --> 32:28.250
-What's it called?
-Doesn't have a name.

32:28.424 --> 32:30.165
-Why not?
-Has to be secret.

32:30.339 --> 32:31.558
That's what they tell you
when you join.

32:31.732 --> 32:32.951
What do you do?

32:33.125 --> 32:35.692
I can't tell you
till you're in the gang.

32:35.866 --> 32:38.565
-How many of you are there?
-Not allowed to say.

32:38.739 --> 32:40.480
What do you have to do
to join, then?

32:40.654 --> 32:43.004
Whatever they tell you.

32:43.178 --> 32:45.398
If your da's not home
this weekend,

32:45.572 --> 32:46.877
you could come with us.

32:47.052 --> 32:48.227
BUDDY:
I don't know.

32:48.401 --> 32:49.619
I'm trying to practice
my maths.

32:49.793 --> 32:51.578
MOIRA:
Then you're mental. Come on.

32:51.752 --> 32:54.624
If your da's not home anyway,
what else are you gonna do?

