36:10.429 --> 36:11.778
MA:
What have I done?

36:15.695 --> 36:17.914
BUDDY:
All right, Mummy?

36:18.088 --> 36:20.700
Why do you always get sad
when a letter comes?

36:21.875 --> 36:24.573
WOMAN: Remember, our
washing powder is biological.

36:26.532 --> 36:28.490
MISS LEWIS:
Come on, Mr. Slowpoke.

36:28.664 --> 36:30.666
Get inside now.

36:30.840 --> 36:33.191
And finally a switch in
the medal positions this week.

36:33.365 --> 36:34.931
Well, Mr. Buddy,
you may not have improved

36:35.105 --> 36:37.456
your handwriting in maths,
for which this once,

36:37.630 --> 36:39.632
in lieu of your intensified
efforts, we will be willing

36:39.806 --> 36:41.111
to give you
the benefit of the doubt,

36:41.286 --> 36:43.766
but you have
improved your score.

36:43.940 --> 36:47.509
